3
00:00:09,180 --> 00:00:13,800
Good morning. I'm Jeanine Herbst, from NPR  News, and here are today's top stories:

4
00:00:13,800 --> 00:00:18,000
Former President Donald Trump is  expected to turn himself in to  

5
