Trump faces 13 felony counts for an alleged  effort to overturn Georgia's 2020 election:

7
00:00:30,420 --> 00:00:34,620
"In some ways, Trump will be like every  other defendant who stepped foot into the  

8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:39,420
Fulton County Jail: He'll be formally arrested,  fingerprinted and processed after being charged  

9
00:00:39,420 --> 00:00:43,020
last week. But the former president,  who is under Secret Service protection,  

10
00:00:43,020 --> 00:00:47,880
also was expected to have a booking photo taken  — the first one in the four different indictments  

11
00:00:47,880 --> 00:00:52,680
he's received in the last few months. After  upstaging the GOP presidential debate last  

12
